text: Permyaki () is a rural locality (a selo) in Petropavlovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 171 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km west from Petropavlovsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Permyaki
